_GEng_SpriteToPoint_AngleDiff:
Returns the angle between a Sprite Object and a point,

_GEng_SpriteToSprite_Vector: Returns a vector oriented from a Sprite Object to another
_GEng_AngleToVector: Returns a vector from an Angle and a Lenght
